OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has said the
OL,7,Fbin strikes have gone on for "too
OL,8,Flong" and its door "remains open" to
OL,9,Ffind a resolution.
OL,11,FIt comes exactly a year after members
OL,12,Fof the union Unite started an
OL,13,Findefinite walkout in a dispute over
OL,14,Fpay, with little sign of a
OL,15,Fbreakthrough in the deadlocked row.
OL,17,FThe union says planned reforms of the
OL,18,Frefuse collection service will lead to
OL,19,Fhundreds of its members losing
OL,20,Fthousands of pounds in yearly pay.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
