OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,FThe council denies the claim and is
OL,7,Fpressing ahead with changes it says
OL,8,Fare needed to improve the service.
OL,10,FThe government has urged both sides in
OL,11,Fthe long-running Birmingham bin strike
OL,12,Fto bring the dispute to an end.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Communities and
OL,15,FLocal Government Department said:
OL,16,F"Resolving the strike is a matter for
OL,17,Fthe council.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
