PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773302722
OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,F"But getting back to serving local
OL,7,Fresidents must remain a priority and
OL,8,Fwe urge all parties to bring this
OL,9,Fdispute to an end."
OL,11,FCouncillor Majid Mahmood, Birmingham
OL,12,FCity Council's cabinet member for
OL,13,Fenvironment and transport, said: "The
OL,14,Fbin strike in Birmingham has gone on
OL,15,Ffor too long.
OL,17,F"I'm sorry for the disruption this has
OL,18,Fcaused, and I would hope Unite would
OL,19,Falso want to apologise.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]uD@bOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773302722
OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,F"It isn't good enough and we want to
OL,7,Fend the dispute.
OL,9,F"But let us be clear, the council has
OL,10,Fmade a series of offers to Unite to
OL,11,Fend the strike, but they have all been
OL,12,Frejected.
OL,14,F"We are moving ahead with the
OL,15,Fimplementation of the improved waste
OL,16,Fservice this summer, a service that
OL,17,Fhas been poor for too long.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
