PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773302722
OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,F"This will see the rollout of food
OL,7,Fwaste collections from June this year
OL,8,Fon a phased basis, along with the
OL,9,Freturn of improved recycling and green
OL,10,Fwaste collection services.
OL,12,F"This will happen regardless of the
OL,13,Fsituation with industrial action to
OL,14,Fgive the people of Birmingham the
OL,15,Fwaste service they deserve.
OL,17,F"My message to those still taking
OL,18,Findustrial action is simple: come back
OL,19,Fto work as I want you to be part of
OL,20,Fthis new and improved service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
