OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773302722
OL,3,C'It isn't good enough': Council says
OL,4,Cit wants end to bin strikes one year on
OL,6,F"Our door remains open."
OL,8,FThe council said a "new, improved
OL,9,Fservice" will roll out in the summer,
OL,10,Fadding that its contingency plan was
OL,11,Fensuring that every household gets a
OL,12,Fweekly waste collection.
OL,14,FDespite the ongoing industrial action,
OL,15,Fthe authority said it is collecting
OL,16,Fwaste every week from households, with
OL,17,Fan average of around 1,370 tonnes
OL,18,Fcollected from kerbside every day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@XO]pD@TOUqD@HO]
